prompts.prompt:
Write a business email tailored to the following situation.

Situation: {{SITUATION}}
Sender: {{SENDER_ROLE}}
Recipient: {{RECIPIENT_ROLE}}
Key message: {{KEY_MESSAGE}}
Desired action: {{DESIRED_ACTION}}

Please include:
- Subject line (3 options)
- Body (professional business tone)
- Signature template

Max length: {{LENGTH}} characters

Create landing page copy for the following product or service.

Product name: {{PRODUCT_NAME}}
USP (unique selling proposition): {{USP}}
Target customer: {{TARGET_CUSTOMER}}
Price: {{PRICE}}
CTA goal: {{CTA_GOAL}}

Please create:
1. Hero section (headline + subheadline + CTA)
2. Pain-Gain-Solution (PGS) section
3. Features & benefits list (5–7 items)
4. Social proof section (3 customer testimonial templates)
5. FAQ (5 questions)
6. Final CTA section

Create a social media content calendar for the following parameters.

Brand: {{BRAND}}
Platforms: {{PLATFORMS}}
Period: {{PERIOD}}
Content themes: {{THEMES}}
Posting frequency: {{FREQUENCY}}

For each post, provide:
- Post date and time
- Content format (text / image / video / reel)
- Caption
- Hashtags (10–15)
- Image prompt (for Midjourney / DALL-E)
- Engagement CTA

Design an optimal System Prompt for Claude for the following use case.

Use case: {{USE_CASE}}
Persona: {{PERSONA}}
Main tasks: {{MAIN_TASKS}}
Constraints: {{CONSTRAINTS}}
Output format: {{OUTPUT_FORMAT}}

Please design:
1. Role definition (clear persona setup)
2. Capabilities and skills declaration
3. Behavioral guidelines
4. Constraints and prohibitions
5. Output format specification
6. Few-shot examples (3)
7. Error handling instructions

Output the final System Prompt in complete, ready-to-use form.
